    ALSA: usx2y: Fix unlocked snd_pcm_stop() call
    
    snd_pcm_stop() must be called in the PCM substream lock context.
    
    Cc: <stable@vger.kernel.org>
    Signed-off-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

